{"tid":2021222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2021年中學文憑試歷史科漏出","createTime":"2020-05-17T15:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T15:04:53.000Z","uid":328737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad950d8ed9e84eb25298068a1fe73df802771060","tid":2021222,"uid":328737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"1). 教育局日前要求考評局，取消中學文憑試歷史科涉及日本侵華試題，引發社會爭議。《人民日報》的應用程式發佈署名文章，指事件再次證明香港教育界「中毒至深」，香港教育問題十分嚴重，又斥考評局事後發的聲明「回應傲慢、表態曖昧」，事件揭示教育界「不乏害群之馬」，教育體制已如「無掩雞籠」。文章指，為了拯救孩子和未來，必須對香港教育來一次「徹底的刮骨療毒」，進行「大刀闊斧」 改革，並找出隱藏在教材和其他地方的「毒內容」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E8%BD%9F%E8%80%83%E8%A9%95%E5%B1%80%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%82%B2%E6%85%A2-%E4%BF%83%E5%B0%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-%E5%BE%B9%E5%BA%95%E5%88%AE%E9%AA%A8%E7%99%82%E6%AF%92-%E6%89%BE%E5%87%BA-%E6%AF%92%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9-%E7%9B%AF%E4%BD%8F%E6%92%AD%E6%AF%92%E8%80%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%25BD%259F%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2582%25B2%25E6%2585%25A2-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2-%25E5%25BE%25B9%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2588%25AE%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%2599%2582%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E6%2589%25BE%25E5%2587%25BA-%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9-%25E7%259B%25AF%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592%25E8%2580%2585%2F&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=9cf3117b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%25BD%259F%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2582%25B2%25E6%2585%25A2-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2-%25E5%25BE%2